      <p><strong>Training Location:</strong> Grand Rapids, MN</p>
      <p><strong>Practice Times:</strong> See calendar for details</p>
      <p><strong>Equipment:</strong> Team pricing available</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
